<section xml:id="sec-5-4-Factor-Root_Theorem" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Factor-Root Theorem</title>
    <p>The <em>Factor-Root Theorem</em> establishes the connection between roots of a polynomial and the factors of the polynomial. 
        The connection between roots and <m>x</m>-intercepts is discussed and some advanced factoring of polynomials is shown, 
        without the full details of <em>Polynomial Long Division</em>.</p>
        
